text: Ramos Saozinho Ribeiro Maxanches (born 12 April 1994),https://int.soccerway.com/players/ramos-saozinho-ribeiro- maxanches/271097/ also known as Ramos Maxanches, is a football player who currently plays as goalkeeper for Timor-Leste national football team. ==International career== Ramos made his senior international debut against Brunei national football team in the 2014 AFF Suzuki Cup qualification on 12 October 2014.http://www.national-football- teams.com/matches/report/11489/East_Timor_Brunei.htmlhttps://int.soccerway.com/matches/2014/10/12/asia/asean- football-championship/timor-leste/brunei-darussalam/1882107/ ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:East Timorese footballers Category:Timor-Leste international footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Footballers at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for East Timor
